Your task is to guide me step-by-step to build a production-ready SaaS web application called:

AI-Powered Hardware Business Assistant

This system must be architected for:
- Real early-stage users
- Clean collaborpasted5:53 PMAI-Powered Hardware Business Assistant — Full Build Guide
I'll act as your technical co-founder. Let's build this systematically. I'll cover everything end-to-end, with copy-paste-ready code.

PART 1: SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE OVERVIEW
How the System Fits Together
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    CLIENT LAYER                          │
│  React (Vite) + Tailwind → Vercel CDN                   │
│  .env.local / .env.production → dynamic API base URL    │
└────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────┘
                     │ HTTPS + JWT Bearer Token
┌────────────────────▼────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   BACKEND LAYER                          │
│  Spring Boot 3 (Java 17) → Railway/Render               │
│  Spring Security → JWT Filter → Role-Based Access       │
│  REST Controllers → Services → Repositories             │
└──────┬──────────┬────────────┬───────────────┬──────────┘
       │          │            │               │
  PostgreSQL  Claude API  Africa's Talking   Paystack/Stripe
  (Managed)  (AI Insights)  (SMS)           (Payments)
