### What Your Final Structure Looks Like
```
hardware-assistant-frontend/
├── public/
├── src/
│   ├── api/             ← Axios instance + API calls per domain
│   ├── components/      ← Reusable UI components
│   ├── context/         ← AuthContext (global auth state)
│   ├── hooks/           ← Custom hooks
│   ├── pages/           ← Route-level page components
│   ├── router/          ← AppRouter + ProtectedRoute
│   ├── utils/           ← Helpers (localStorage, formatting)
│   ├── App.jsx
│   ├── main.jsx
│   └── index.css        ← Tailwind directives
├── .env.local
├── .env.development
├── .env.staging
├── .env.production
├── tailwind.config.js
├── vite.config.js
└── package.json

Quick Reference: Commands You'll Use Daily
CommandWhat it doesnpm run devStart dev server on port 5173npm run buildProduction buildnpm run build:stagingStaging buildnpm run previewPreview the production build locallynpm run lintCheck for code issues

